bb12196f-e08a-5608-a307-d418ada105d0,tg:rubgr:2679,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"1 zw/w foto. [Notitie FG]: Drawing for Euntes in Emaus (Bastelaer 14), Lebeer 9. Berlin, 'Bruegel als Zeichner, 1975, N° 37. Sold at Christie's 29-11, 1977, lot 158 (280 x 413 mm) to Koninklijk Museum, Antwerp for £ 28000. As 'The Property of a West German collector' (i.o. Professor Dr. Ingenieur H. Schenck). To the exhibitions and Literature mentioned in the Christie (which has a very good reproduction of the drawing though too small on the left) should be added: Aachen, Suermondt-Museum, Alte niederländische Kunst in Aachen, exh. Oct.-Nov. 1973, Cat.N° 35, Slg. Prof.dr. Ing. H. Schenck: Pieter Bruegel d.Ä. Die Emmausgänger, 26,3 x 41 cm. Feder auf Papier. J.G. van Gelder adds as Prov.: a) jonkheer Jan van der Does (Friend of Huygens II, who collected Bruegel drawings); b) Valerius Röver, recorded in his coll. Portfolio 24: Groot Landschap, waarin 3 beeldjes als pelgrims met de pen op geelachtig pap(ier), waarna de print is gesneden met de gemelde collectie.",descriptive note,Nederlands,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

column4: <content>1 zw/w foto. [Notitie FG]: Drawing for Euntes in Emaus (Bastelaer 14), Lebeer 9. Berlin, 'Bruegel als Zeichner, 1975, N° 37. Sold at Christie's 29-11, 1977, lot 158 (280 x 413 mm) to Koninklijk Museum, Antwerp for £ 28000. As 'The Property of a West German collector' (i.o. Professor Dr. Ingenieur H. Schenck). To the exhibitions and Literature mentioned in the Christie (which has a very good reproduction of the drawing though too small on the left) should be added: Aachen, Suermondt-Museum, Alte niederländische Kunst in Aachen, exh. Oct.-Nov. 1973, Cat.N° 35, Slg. Prof.dr. Ing. H. Schenck: Pieter Bruegel d.Ä. Die Emmausgänger, 26,3 x 41 cm. Feder auf Papier. J.G. van Gelder adds as Prov.: a) jonkheer Jan van der Does (Friend of Huygens II, who collected Bruegel drawings); b) Valerius Röver, recorded in his coll. Portfolio 24: Groot Landschap, waarin 3 beeldjes als pelgrims met de pen op geelachtig pap(ier), waarna de print is gesneden met de gemelde collectie.</content>
